text: Great variety of products. Conveniently open *every* day of the year!

(Translated by Google) A very large selection of goods. The store is located between Soho and Chinatown in London.

(Original)
Bardzo duży wybór towarów . Sklep znajduje się pomiędzy Soho a Chinatown w Londynie .
Really good corner shop. Has a good selection of food. Recommend.
